profile:
The Souris Valley Theatre is a non-profit professional musical theatre. The season runs during the summer at our permanent theatre building, Frehlick Hall, in Woodlawn Park in Estevan, Saskatchewan. The season consists of 2 main stage productions. We also host many other events which may include concerts, Fringe shows, childrenâ€™s theatre and other unique events.
Along with producing a dynamic theatre season we also host summer theatre camps for children ages 6 to 18.
name: Souris Valley Theatre
